<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A strong spirituous liqueur made from wormwood and
brandy or alcohol.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Absinthe</qex> makes the tart grow fonder.</q>
<rj><qau>Ernest Dowson</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

